  • Uses of AbstractActionObservation in nusri.fyp.demo.entity

    Fields in nusri.fyp.demo.entity with type parameters of type AbstractActionObservation
    Modifier and Type
    Field
    Description
    private Map<Long,List<AbstractActionObservation>>
    StateMachineLog.observations
    A map of timestamps to action observations.
    This map contains all the action observations that occurred at specific timestamps.
    The key is the timestamp (in milliseconds), and the value is a list of action observations for that timestamp.
    The observations are serialized and deserialized using ActionObservationConverter.
